{"tid":1378092,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各有各做，永不割席！ 730全港不合作運動","createTime":"2019-07-28T15:12:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T19:41:21.000Z","uid":211520,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"544216bfd170c15f9d4d61ef64108d763b525b9b","tid":1378092,"uid":211520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:12:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">7月30號全城不合作運動</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">睇唔過眼政府一次又一次莫視民意，又唔敢出嚟抗爭？<br />\n請立即支持不合作運動</span><br />\n要求政府必須立即回應五大訴求：<br />\n1. 撤回逃犯條例修訂<br />\n2. 收回「暴動」定性<br />\n3. 釋放義士<br />\n4. 追究警隊攬權<br />\n5. 立即推行雙普選<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日不出來，明天出不來</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ioraMRu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FioraMRu.jpg&h=d4cde75d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78938f554bb7d600f6671ac36f63046b80a850c3","tid":1378092,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:39:22.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"2542946b019f46725fbe3f0917d6c82957cda01c","tid":1378092,"uid":211520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:45:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LO8sSX7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLO8sSX7.png&h=b8d66ecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HM2xjC8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHM2xjC8.png&h=6b635c4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CzpPmRt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCzpPmRt.png&h=990351c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yFdTOwu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyFdTOwu.png&h=8d822aa1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd6778085cf0ddf9fdce643ebd525d7dfa886a0e","tid":1378092,"uid":208452,"l